VoltDB NodeJS Wire Protocol Driver 0.1.1

Installation
============

Run "npm -install" to install various node libraries before using the
driver.

Example Application
===================
1. Start the voter example voter example server included in the voltDB 
distribution. It is found VOLTDB_HOME/examples/voter.

2. Execute ./run.sh server

3. Open voternoui.js in the voltdb-client-nodejs directory and make sure 
that the first line of the main method references the host running the 
voter example. The line reads:
 var clusterNodes = ['localhost'];

4. Run the sample
node ./voternoui.js [-c number_of_votes]

Known Issues
============

Driver does not current support varbinary type.